# Example 7: Named texture reference
# All available named textures:
# - rgba_noise  : Multi-octave RGBA noise (most common)
# - gray_noise  : Grayscale fBM noise
# - blue_noise  : Blue noise (good for dithering)
# - wood        : Procedural wood grain
# - abstract    : Colorful Voronoi pattern
